Remotely on the cloud, much faster and efficient than traditional analysis workflows, and giving them the results and data in a fraction of the time.
The platform also utilises cutting-edge technology such as Artificial Intelligence Deep Learning.
*PLEASE NOTE*: The logos in the moodboard (attached in references) are more in line with what we are looking for rather than the logos in the 'Design Inspiration' section. Although the accent colours we would like are bright and vibrant aqua/green.

title: Design a NSFW Logo for Male Body Wash Brand That Fight Back Traditional Toxic Masculinity
description:

Our mission is to provide men body wash to anyone who'd like their body to smell good, fight back the stereotype of toxic masculinity. Round 2 purpose is to create a product that every male wanted to start his day with, a product that makes them feel great and smells great in the process.
The target audience is males aged 23-to 38. Education level: College and above. Income: medium class and above. Our research showed that 80% who bought body wash are male, 20% are female. (40% of males are from the LGBT group)
